---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Unindexed Object | Ayue Observatory"
  description="这个地址尚未被 Ayue Observatory 索引为 Archive Object。"
>
  <main class="content-page not-found-page">
    <section class="not-found-panel" aria-labelledby="not-found-title">
      <p class="eyebrow">Unindexed Object</p>
      <h1 id="not-found-title">未索引对象</h1>
      <p>
        这个地址还没有进入 Ayue Observatory 的档案索引。它可能尚未被整理为 Archive Object，
        也可能已经移动到新的编号位置。
      </p>
      <div class="not-found-actions" aria-label="返回入口">
        <a href="/archive"><span>01</span><strong>返回档案</strong></a>
        <a href="/"><span>02</span><strong>回到首页</strong></a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .not-found-page {
    display: grid;
    min-height: calc(100vh - 90px);
    place-items: center;
  }

  .not-found-panel {
    border-left: 1px solid var(--color-border-soft);
    max-width: 760px;
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .not-found-panel::before {
    background: var(--color-accent);
    content: '';
    height: 5rem;
    left: -1px;
    opacity: 0.72;
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    width: 1px;
  }

  .not-found-panel h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 6rem);
    line-height: 1;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .not-found-panel p:last-of-type {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.08rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    margin: 1.4rem 0 0;
    max-width: 620px;
  }

  .not-found-actions {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-soft);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-soft);
    display: grid;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .not-found-actions a {
    align-items: center;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-soft);
    display: grid;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    gap: 0.8rem;
    grid-template-columns: 2.5rem minmax(0, 1fr);
    padding: 0.9rem 0;
  }

  .not-found-actions a:first-child {
    border-top: 0;
  }

  .not-found-actions span {
    color: var(--color-meta);
    font-size: var(--text-meta);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-meta);
  }

  .not-found-actions strong {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-meta);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
</style>
